name: Turtle-iffic-topia
description:
A beautiful world where animals can hang out and have fun virtually!

-> Make a character in the Character Design Studio
-> Make a lil' virtual house and move into one of 2 luxurious neighborhoods
-> Play games, travel, and take a Zoom selfie with animal buddies

We hope you have a turtle-iffic time! Let us know how it goes!
